    "selected_writer_rationale": "silver.usp_load_dimmultiwriter_full is the primary writer because it independently rebuilds the DimMultiWriter dimension table from scratch via TRUNCATE + INSERT from bronze.Product. The delta (upsert via MERGE) and archive (soft-delete via UPDATE) procedures are supplementary operational passes that require the full loader to have established the table structure first. For dbt migration purposes, the full loader represents the authoritative transformation logic.",
